 Further template category notes 

 This category contains pages in the template namespace. It should not be used to categorize articles or pages in other namespaces.  To add a template to this category: 
If the template has a separate documentation page (usually called "Template:template name/doc"), add [[Category:Pagename manipulation templates]]to the <includeonly> section at the bottom of that page. Otherwise, add <noinclude>[[Category:Pagename manipulation templates]]</noinclude>to the end of the template code, making sure it starts on the same line as the code's last character.
